---
import Container from '../../components/Container.astro';
import Heading from '../../components/Heading.astro';
import Section from '../../components/Section.astro';
---

<Section id="about">
  <Container>
    <Heading
      highlight={['Vayne Myko']}
      title="Who is Vayne Myko?"
      subtitle="A digital blacksmith on a mission to build a community of digital artisans"
      position="center"
    />
    <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-8">
      <p class="flex-1">
        <strong>Hey, I'm Vayne Myko.</strong>
        <br />
        <br />
        <strong
          >I'm a Digital Blacksmith and I help other creators and businesses get
          off the ground.</strong
        >
        <br />
        <br />
        I'm the person other people reach out to when they feel lost on their creator
        or business journey, experiences, vision, mindset, lifestyle, and productivity.
        <br />
        <br />
        I help them break down difficult topics into easily digestable pieces, refine
        their vision, and help them push their business so they could earn more while
        working less hours by methodically increasing productivity.
        <br />
        <br />
        Whenever someone wants to start their online journey as a creator or a business,
        I help them find their <strong>archetype</strong> and create systems for
        success.
      </p>
      <div class="flex-1 relative group">
        <div
          class="bg-zinc-500 h-[600px] flex-1 card relative overflow-hidden z-10 transition-transform hover:scale-[1.02]"
        >
          <!-- <Image src={MyImage} alt="image" class="absolute inset-0" /> -->
        </div>

        <div
          class="bg-primary h-[600px] card absolute transition-transform translate-x-2 translate-y-2 group-hover:translate-x-3 group-hover:translate-y-3 inset-0"
        >
        </div>
        <div
          class="bg-secondary h-[600px] card absolute transition-transform -translate-x-2 -translate-y-2 group-hover:-translate-x-3 group-hover:-translate-y-3 inset-0"
        >
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="flex-1">
        Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit, sed do eiusmod
        tempor incididunt ut labore et dolore magna aliqua. Ut enim ad minim
        veniam, quis nostrud exercitation ullamco laboris nisi ut aliquip ex ea
        commodo consequat. Duis aute irure dolor in reprehenderit in voluptate
        velit esse cillum dolore eu fugiat nulla pariatur. Excepteur sint
        occaecat cupidatat non proident, sunt in culpa qui officia deserunt
        mollit anim id est laborum
      </div>
    </div>
  </Container>
</Section>
